1. *Razmislila* sam o tome i odlučila da neću ići na žurku. (I thought about it and decided not to go to the party.)
2. Molim te, *razmisli* dobro pre nego što doneseš tu odluku. (Please, think carefully before you make that decision.)
3. Da bi uspeo u životu, moraš *razmišljati* pozitivno. (To succeed in life, you need to think positively.)
4. On je brzo *razmislio* i pronašao rešenje za taj problem. (He quickly thought and found a solution to that problem.)
5. *Razmislite* malo o tome pre nego što mi odgovorite. (Think about it a little before you answer me.)
6. Žao mi je, ali ne mogu *razmisliti* o tome sada. (I'm sorry, but I can't think about it right now.)
7. Nema potrebe da *razmišljate* o tome, ja ću se pobrinuti za sve. (There's no need for you to think about it, I'll take care of everything.)
8. *Razmišljajte* pozitivno i sve će se na kraju rešiti. (Think positively and everything will be resolved in the end.)
9. Oni su *razmišljali* zajedno i došli do sjajnog plana. (They thought together and came up with a great plan.)
10. Molim te, *razmisli* šta bi uradio na mom mestu. (Please, think about what you would do in my place.)